      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Groton%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "In 1849, Charles and Lyman Perrigo started the first blast furnace and machine factories that helped shape Groton’s early industry.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        6
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://www.grotonny.gov/historical-facts"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "The town’s first library opened in 1834, making Groton one of the earliest communities in the Finger Lakes region to establish a public lending library.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
